codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Saccus quī hīc est = h~ saccus. Choose from this set of possible answers [ ic, aec, oc, ae aec, od oc, ī ic] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-001' where ANSWER in [ 'ic', 'aec', 'oc', 'ae aec', 'od oc', 'ī ic']
